title: [Rumor Woods, Canine Track]
[Rumor Woods, Equid Track]
description: Roughly carved poles stand high above the stables, each one strung with a wolf-sewn pennant of crimson and ebon hues.  The hay-strewn path leads up to a wide door, the entrance surrounded by worn-out saddles, dulled lances, and other equipment switched out between contests.

Roughly carved poles stand high above the stables, each one strung with a stag-sewn pennant of gold and green hues.  The hay-strewn path leads up to a wide door, the entrance surrounded by worn-out saddles, dulled lances, and other equipment switched out between contests.

Roughly carved poles stand high above the stables, each one strung with a phoenix-sewn pennant of vermilion and black.  The hay-strewn path leads up to a wide door, the entrance surrounded by worn-out saddles, dulled lances, and other equipment switched out between contests.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, west, northwest
